Q: networkIdle
    It waits until no network requests are pending for 500ms.
    await page.waitForLoadState('networkidle');
    Used when:
    page loads multiple APIs
    SPA applications
    dynamic content loading

Q: How do you take screenshots?
    Full page:
    await page.screenshot({ path: 'page.png', fullPage: true });

    Element screenshot:
    await page.locator('#logo').screenshot({ path: 'logo.png' });

    Automatic screenshot on failure:
    use: {
      screenshot: 'only-on-failure'
    }

Q: How do you handle iframes in Playwright?
    Using frameLocator.
    Example:
    const frame = page.frameLocator('#iframeId');
    await frame.locator('#submit').click();

    Alternative:
    const frame = page.frame({ name: 'frameName' });

